    <item>
      <title>因美联储观点和日本地震，日经 225 指数在第一个交易日下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/nikkei-225-falls-on-first-trading-day-on-fed-view-japan-quake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本日经 225 指数创下两周来最大跌幅，原因是市场猜测美联储将在较长时间内维持高利率，从而损害科技股，而且元旦当天西北地区发生的强烈地震拖累了一些公司。东证指数上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/nikkei-225-falls-on-first-trading-day-on-fed-view-japan-quake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:31:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
